Variable:
========
Normally we can use
vars:
   - x: 5
   - y: 10 
tasks:
   vars: x  --> if you define vars keyword it will tacken the value of the vriasble x . This is one method
vars01-example.yml 


Now  we can usee mse keyword to display the  string values , inbetween i want to call and display the value 
of  my variables, we can do like the below, This is called string interpolation.



- hosts: all
  vars:
   - x: 100
   - y: 200
  tasks:
   - debug:
      msg: "Hi Saba How are you doing today, Today i have yearned {{ x }} take care Bye as of Now" 

